code: import httpClient from'../common/http_common';import{httpClientPut,httpClientDelete,httpClientPost}from'../common/http_common';var getAll=function getAll(){return httpClient.get("/hotels");};var getByPage=function getByPage(page){var search=arguments.length>1&&arguments[1]!==undefined?arguments[1]:"";return httpClient.get("/hotels/page/".concat(page,"?search=").concat(search));};var create=function create(data){return httpClientPost.post("/hotels",data);};var get=function get(id){return httpClient.get("/hotels/detail/".concat(id));};var getTop=function getTop(id){return httpClient.get("/hotels/top/".concat(id));};var update=function update(id,data){return httpClientPut.put("/hotels/".concat(id),data);};var remove=function remove(id){return httpClientDelete.delete("/hotels/".concat(id));};var logger={getAll:getAll,get:get,getByPage:getByPage,getTop:getTop,update:update,remove:remove,create:create};export default logger;
